describe users;
+-------+------------------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
| Field | Type                   | Null | Key | Default | Extra          |
+-------+------------------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
| id    | int                    | NO   | PRI | NULL    | auto_increment |
| name  | varchar(40)            | NO   | UNI | NULL    |                |
| type  | enum('admin','normal') | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
+-------+------------------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+

describe categories;
+-------+-------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
| Field | Type        | Null | Key | Default | Extra          |
+-------+-------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
| id    | int         | NO   | PRI | NULL    | auto_increment |
| name  | varchar(40) | NO   | UNI | NULL    |                |
+-------+-------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+


